      "content": "paths forward? there aren't any. i've lost everything. my funding, my reputation, my purpose... even my friends only know me as 'the researcher'. without the work, i'm just a ghost. i'm just so incredibly exhausted by the effort of existing in this version of my life. it's like i'm drowning and everyone is just telling me to keep swimming when there's no shore in sight.",
